: 6px solid rgb(71, 193, 168);border-top-color: rgb(71, 193, 168);border-right-color: rgb(71, 193, 168);box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="height: 100%;width: 24px;float: right;border-bottom: 6px solid rgb(71, 193, 168);border-right: 6px solid rgb(71, 193, 168);border-top-color: rgb(71, 193, 168);border-left-color: rgb(71, 193, 168);box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><section class="V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: right;margin-bottom: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 13px;box-sizing: border-box;">文章来源：智研咨询</span></p></section></section></section><section class="V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 0.8em;height: 0.8em;line-height: 1;padding: 2px;border-left: 2px solid rgb(71, 193, 168);border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(71, 193, 168);transform: rotate(-45deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(-45deg);-moz-transform: rotate(-45deg);-o-transform: rotate(-45deg);border-top-color: rgb(71, 193, 168);border-right-color: rgb(71, 193, 168);box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section><section class="V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;"><img data-ratio="0.6361789" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/bibQQKblOtyqnl4u0sDUC0MMOyia5CGpjSuxOCaurBcxkoicSWsSKzLicU072tiaPFygiakcefd6rXIg62WlGKYic12sw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="492" style="vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;"  /></section></section></section><section class="V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;margin-bottom: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 13px;box-sizing: border-box;">2011-2017年我国铅锌矿探明储量（万吨）</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;">据国家统计局数据，全国1-4月铅精矿产量为51.7万金属吨，同比减少1.3%。2018年1-4月国内铅精矿进口量约为16.8万金属吨，下降约20%。铅精矿进口量下降主要是受到停止进口朝鲜精矿的影响，国内铅精矿短缺23.6万吨。精炼铅方面，1-4月国内精铅产量为140.5万吨，同比下降8.8%，我们认为国内趋严的环保政策对铅冶炼造成较强的冲击。2017年铅下游消费86%主要集中在铅酸蓄电池，其需求增速呈现下降趋势。</p></section></section></section><section class="V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;"><img data-ratio="0.3836806" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/bibQQKblOtyqnl4u0sDUC0MMOyia5CGpjSOyCF6hfJHeq3wKgTdJSaBeSk0qpqjemFC30gj3ib0aoI8fnhhI8juTA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="576" style="vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;"  /></section></section></section><section class="V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;margin-bottom: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 13px;box-sizing: border-box;">全球铅精矿、精铅市场供需格局（单位：万吨）</span></p></section></section></section><section class="V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;"><img data-ratio="0.6295547" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/bibQQKblOtyqnl4u0sDUC0MMOyia5CGpjSlBTiaBx9qK22bUppkn3uA6AichsK9rx2wpqyN9PzTYichFWZ1VcfQXibJg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="494" style="vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;"  /></section></section></section><section class="V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;margin-bottom: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 13px;box-sizing: border-box;">2017年铅下游消费结构</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;">铅酸蓄电池广泛应用于汽车、摩托车、通信、新能源、交通、电力等众多领域。近年我国铅酸蓄电池进出口数量及金额呈波动趋势，2017年铅酸蓄电池产品进口量577万个，出口量4782万个，进口额3.25亿美元，出口额26.86亿美元。</p></section></section></section><section class="V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;"><img data-ratio="0.6252546" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/bibQQKblOtyqnl4u0sDUC0MMOyia5CGpjSybu0INOPPC6u9kJctmD26woicwQUwtSOha4dZmkM0UgDKZyR4icVtWOA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="491" style="vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;"  /></section></section></section><section class="V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;margin-bottom: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 13px;box-sizing: border-box;">2011-2017年我国铅酸蓄电池进出口数量分析</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;">在全球市场范围内，铅酸蓄电池由于其技术成熟、安全性高、循环再生利用率高、适用温带宽、电压稳定、组合一致性好及价格低廉等优势，在电池市场占据主导地位。2017年，全球铅酸蓄电池市场规模约为429亿美元，同比增长0.7%。</p></section></section></section><section class="V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box;"><img data-ratio="0.6376518" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/bibQQKblOtyqnl4u0sDUC0MMOyia5CGpjSrUXQhZIu3wolciaymMPTwdTM3qmmMQILK9LtM7xicrLCwDn2lKiazWZyw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="494" style="vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;"  /></section></section></section><section class="V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;margin-bottom: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 13px;box-sizing: border-box;">2011-2017年全球铅酸蓄电池市场规模分析</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;">我国铅污染事件的高发态势，一是电池生产环节铅污染物超标排放问题突出，二是回收无序导致含铅废酸污染严重，三是铅再生利用不规范导致大量二次污染。提高环保水平，有效解决企业生产过程中的重金属污染问题，对推动铅冶炼行业持续健康发展具有重大积极意义。</p><p style="margin-bottom: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;"><br  /></p><section style="padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;white-space: normal;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.8;box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="V5" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(71, 193, 168);box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">·END·</strong></span></p></section></section></section><section class="V5" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="padding: 3px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="padding-top: 6px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-bottom: -6px;border-top: 1px solid rgb(71, 193, 168);border-right-color: rgb(71, 193, 168);border-bottom-color: rgb(71, 193, 168);border-left-color: rgb(71, 193, 168);box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="float: left;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 10px;height: 10px;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(71, 193, 168);transform: rotate(45deg);background-color: rg